      "level": 2,
      "text": "Meet us at the leading conferences we attend and sponsor"
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Participating in and sponsoring the BrightonSEO conference has already become a big tradition of ours. If you decide to go, visit our stand to see the new tools we’ve released!"
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Each year, we travel to the Netherlands to attend the Friends of Search conference. It brings together industry leaders who are passionate about sharing what they know about ecommerce SEO, E-A-T, technical SEO, etc."
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "This unique UK-based conference celebrates women and non-binary professionals in tech SEO. We’re proud to join and contribute to this insightful and collaborative platform."
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Join SE Ranking at this key conference for professionals in the ecommerce sector. Explore the latest trends and tools in ecommerce SEO while networking with industry experts."
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "SE Ranking regularly participates in this US-hosted optimization & digital marketing conference. Join us at this must-attend event buzzing with the latest industry insights and trends."
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Connect with SE Ranking at the International Search Summit in Spain. This event specializes in international SEO strategies. You’ll get tons of insights into global search trends and techniques here."
    },
